%e A227437 Longest win on an 8 X 8 chessboard: Ka1 Sa2 Sb1 Sg1 - Kf2, 1.Sg1-h3! Kf2-g3! 2.Sh3-g5! Kg3-f4! 3.Sg5-f7! Kf4-g3 4.Ka1-b2 Kg3-f4 5.Kb2-c2 Kf4-g3 6.Kc2-d2 Kg3-f4 7.Sb1-a3 Kf4-f3 8.Kd2-d3 Kf3-f4! 9.Sa3-c4 Kf4-f5! 10.Sc4-e5 Kf5-f4 11.Sa2-b4 Kf4-f5! 12.Sb4-c6 Kf5-e6 13.Kd3-e4! Ke6-f6! 14.Sc6-d4! Kf6-e7 15.Ke4-f5! Ke7-f8! 16.Kf5-e6! Kf8-g7 17.Sd4-f5! Kg7-f8 18.Se5-g6! Kf8-g8! 19.Ke6-f6! Kg8-h7! 20.Sf7-g5! Kh7-g8! 21.Sf5-e7#, therefore a(8) = 21.
